page.title: 12A DAY IN THE LIFE OF ME
page.content: On a normal day at home I get up at about 7.45 and I go down stairs for breakfast.For breakfast I usually have the breakfast cereal called start.It takes me about 20 minutes to eat it.When I have finished my breakfast I go upstairs and I do my weight training and press_ups. After that I get washed and dressed.After 9.30 I am allowed to go out side because it is not so early.I go out on my bike and I knock for James and David.We usually go down to our camp in the trees every day.We play there all morning and have lots of fun.At about 12.30 I head back towards home so that I can start our lunch.For lunch on a normal weekend I usually have for dinner 5 sausages, some baked beans and a fried egg. I go outside again and play all afternoon. At 6.30 I have tea.At 8.45 I go to bed. ]
